description.name: SAWMILL RIDGE
description.text: Sawmill Ridge in Dublin, OH offers spacious 1 and 2 bedroom apartment homes for rent. Sawmill Ridge is a pet friendly community located within the Dublin City School District. Amenities include a swimming pool with sundeck, updated appliance packages, and gas fireplaces. Sawmill Ridge could not be closer to endless options for dining, shopping and entertainment in the Dublin area as well as the new Bridge Street District. We are conveniently located off 270 and Sawmill Road while providing a private and scenic living environment. Spend the summer months relaxing on our pool deck, spending time on your enclosed patio/covered porch, or enjoying our two acre park.
